        List<? extends SampledEdge> getEdges()
        Description copied from interface: Vertex
        Returns the list of edges connected to this vertex. Although, the returned collection is a list, it must not contain duplicate entries. The list implementation should implement the RandomAccess interface to allow fast iterating over the collection.
